This project follows **Modular Architecture** principles with **BLoC pattern** for state management, organized into feature modules with shared components.

### Core Principles
- **Separation of Concerns**: Data, Domain, and UI layers are clearly separated
- **Dependency Rule**: Inner layers (domain) don't depend on outer layers (UI/data)
- **Modular Design**: Features are isolated in modules for scalability
